===============================
README: 
1. Running the program
2. Running the C++ unittests
3. Compiling the C++ code 
===============================

## 1. Running the programm

cd build
day04_part1 ../boards.txt < ../random-numbers.txt


## 2. Running the C++ unittests

cd build
./test_day04_part1 < ../test-random-numbers.txt


## 3. Compiling the C++ code 

Note: We tell CMake to generate a build.ninja file (instead of a Makefile)

cd build
cmake -GNinja ..
ninja

Note: ninja does the actual compiling (and linking)

